\layout Abstract

An exploration of the interior or the Mandelbrot Set and its relationship
 to the Dedekind eta function.
 This provides yet another example of the close interconnection between
 the structure of the Modular Group and fractals,and specifically connects
 modular forms to structures inside of the Mandelbrot set.
\layout Abstract

This paper is part of a set of chapters that explore the relationship between
 the real numbers, the modular group, and fractals.
